{"tid":578933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴輸波的最大原因","createTime":"2018-03-03T06:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T18:24:50.000Z","uid":55851,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"262932c02f850c14ad79b3a4926ec3a4ee68154a","tid":578933,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"我最主要就係想指一阿仙奴輸波的最大原因，當然球員和教練都有一定的責任，但我認為最大的問題是反雲的那幫人，我上社交網站上看到，他們日日都在評擊雲加，是阿仙奴輸波的關鍵！如果不喜歡雲加的話，就請支持其他球隊，為什麼日日都想希望雲加輸波？雲加這十季的成績大幅下滑，都是因為那班反雲的7頭日日在咀咒雲加輸波，而最不幸的是，竟然連個天都幫埋佢地，搞到雲加教得咁差。<br />\n<br />\n唉！我明白有批評才有進步，但現在的雲加，真的很需要各隊球迷的支持，才能重震雄風！請停止對雲加的批評或咀咒，並關閉其有關的專頁和網站！雲加成績下滑最要主原因是反雲人士不斷的干擾，如果他們的不停止反雲行動的話，那就消滅他們吧！只有這樣做才可以令阿仙奴做番一隊英超BIG 4！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/wenger_always_optimistic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F05%2Fwenger_always_optimistic.gif&h=91e0eeef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"076cb30db5f1209d2545124b997e0b53f642f429","tid":578933,"uid":5843,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:21:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢囉on9</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c8afbf648fa14ab46ce88a9411e749d08e92b61","tid":578933,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"反雲應該皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"088e68daa7b7c85f49a8a3d49874d82f54b09937","tid":578933,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢囉on9</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aea66cb4de3dc7fde4e62bd9a01ccceade1e7b54","tid":578933,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"088e68daa7b7c85f49a8a3d49874d82f54b09937","tid":578933,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>